        }
      ],
      "content": "Together, the Decentralized Operations Platform and the Builder Platform form the digital substrate of the Powerhouse model. The Operations Platform provides scaffolding for work: roles, rules, payments, and projects. The Builder Platform enables the ecosystem to evolve: by building, sharing, and monetizing new capabilities. They are not products to be sold -- they are foundational infrastructure for a new kind of organization. Powerhouse describes itself as building the operating system for a post-corporate world.",
